{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "eicher-app-v2-2026",
    "name": "🚛 Eicher Driver App",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Eicher (main truck) Driver mobile app.\n\n**Role required:** `driver eicher`\n\n**E2E Flow:**\n1. Login → capture token\n2. Check Today Log → decide whether to show Start Shift screen\n3. POST Start Shift (once per day)\n4. GET Dashboard → note your {{assignmentId}}\n5. Update Transit Status through all 6 steps (DISPATCHED → ARRIVED_AT_DESTINATION)\n6. POST Submit Trip Report (at ARRIVED_AT_DESTINATION)\n7. PATCH End Shift (once per day)\n\n**Status Flow (transitStatus):**\n`DISPATCHED` → `EN_ROUTE_TO_FARM` → `ARRIVED_AT_FARM` → `LOADING` → `IN_TRANSIT_TO_DESTINATION` → `ARRIVED_AT_DESTINATION`\n\n**assignmentStatus auto-promotion:**\nOnce transitStatus moves away from `DISPATCHED`, the backend automatically promotes `assignmentStatus` from `PENDING` → `IN_PROGRESS`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "assignmentId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  var data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (data && data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', data.token);",
                  "    console.log('✅ Eicher token saved:', data.token);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"mobileNo\": \"1000000000\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "users", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login as Eicher Driver. The test script auto-saves the JWT to `{{token}}`.\n\n**Response fields of interest:**\n- `token` — JWT bearer token\n- `user.role` — should be `driver eicher`\n- `user.vehicleId` — the pre-assigned vehicle"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "GET My Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/profile",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "profile"]
            },
            "description": "Returns full driver profile including populated vehicleId (vehicleNumber, vehicleType). Use this to pre-fill the Start Shift form with the default vehicle number."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Daily Log — Shift Start",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Check Today Log Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/daily-logs/check-today",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "daily-logs", "check-today"]
            },
            "description": "🚦 CALL THIS FIRST ON APP OPEN.\n\nReturns whether the current driver has already started their day:\n```json\n// Shift already started:\n{ \"isStarted\": true, \"logId\": \"<ObjectId>\", \"role\": \"driver eicher\" }\n\n// Shift not started yet:\n{ \"isStarted\": false }\n```\n- `isStarted: true`  → skip the meter photo screen, go directly to Dashboard.\n- `isStarted: false` → show the Start Shift / Odometer screen (Step 2)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "POST Start Shift",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "startKm", "value": "46820", "type": "text", "description": "Current odometer reading (km)" },
                { "key": "vehicleNumber", "value": "MH-15-AB-1234", "type": "text", "description": "Vehicle registration number" },
                { "key": "petrolAdvance", "value": "500", "type": "text", "description": "Amount of petrol advance taken (₹). Send 0 if none." },
                { "key": "startKmPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Required — Photo of odometer at start of shift" },
                { "key": "petrolReceiptPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Optional — Photo of petrol receipt if advance taken" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/daily-logs/start",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "daily-logs", "start"]
            },
            "description": "Starts the daily shift log. Each driver can only have ONE active log per day.\n\n**Constraint:** Returns `400` if a log already exists for today — use `check-today` first.\n\n**Response:** The created DailyLog document including `_id` (the logId)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Dashboard",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Driver Dashboard",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/dashboard",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "dashboard"]
            },
            "description": "Returns:\n- `kpis` — counts of active / completed / cancelled assignments scoped to this driver\n- `activeAssignments[]` — all Logistics records where `driverId` OR `pickupDriverId` = this user AND `assignmentStatus` is `PENDING` or `IN_PROGRESS`\n\nEach assignment includes full farmer info, munshi, vehicle details.\n\n👉 Save `activeAssignments[0]._id` into `{{assignmentId}}` to proceed with status updates and trip submission."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "GET My Assignments (Simple List)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/assignments",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "assignments"]
            },
            "description": "Alternative to Dashboard — returns a flat array of active assignment documents (PENDING + IN_PROGRESS). Useful for drop-down assignment picker screens."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Transit Status Updates",
      "description": "Update the live position of the truck in 5 steps. Each PATCH call on the same `{{assignmentId}}` advances the `transitStatus` forward.\n\n⚡ **Auto-promotion:** The first call away from `DISPATCHED` automatically changes `assignmentStatus` from `PENDING` → `IN_PROGRESS`.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Step 1 — EN_ROUTE_TO_FARM",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"transitStatus\": \"EN_ROUTE_TO_FARM\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/assignments/{{assignmentId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "assignments", "{{assignmentId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Driver has left the depot and is heading to the farm.\n\n🔄 `assignmentStatus` auto-promoted: `PENDING` → `IN_PROGRESS`\n🔄 `transitStatus`: `DISPATCHED` → `EN_ROUTE_TO_FARM`"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Step 2 — ARRIVED_AT_FARM",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"transitStatus\": \"ARRIVED_AT_FARM\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/assignments/{{assignmentId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "assignments", "{{assignmentId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Truck has arrived at the farm. The Munshi is now ready to begin loading/packing supervision.\n\n🔄 `transitStatus`: `EN_ROUTE_TO_FARM` → `ARRIVED_AT_FARM`"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Step 3 — LOADING",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"transitStatus\": \"LOADING\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/assignments/{{assignmentId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "assignments", "{{assignmentId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Boxes are being loaded onto the truck. The Munshi will now submit the Packing report.\n\n🔄 `transitStatus`: `ARRIVED_AT_FARM` → `LOADING`"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Step 4 — IN_TRANSIT_TO_DESTINATION",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"transitStatus\": \"IN_TRANSIT_TO_DESTINATION\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/assignments/{{assignmentId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "assignments", "{{assignmentId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Loading is complete. Truck is now in transit to Cold Storage / destination.\n\n🔄 `transitStatus`: `LOADING` → `IN_TRANSIT_TO_DESTINATION`"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Step 5 — ARRIVED_AT_DESTINATION",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"transitStatus\": \"ARRIVED_AT_DESTINATION\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/assignments/{{assignmentId}}/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "assignments", "{{assignmentId}}", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Truck has arrived and unloaded at the destination. Now submit the Trip Report (Step 4).\n\n🔄 `transitStatus`: `IN_TRANSIT_TO_DESTINATION` → `ARRIVED_AT_DESTINATION`"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Trip Report",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Submit Trip Report",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "startRoute", "value": "Coimbatore Depot", "type": "text", "description": "Starting point of the route" },
                { "key": "midRoute", "value": "Salem Bypass", "type": "text", "description": "Optional mid-route stop name" },
                { "key": "destination", "value": "Chennai Cold Storage", "type": "text", "description": "Final delivery destination" },
                { "key": "totalKm", "value": "500", "type": "text", "description": "Total kilometers driven for this trip" },
                { "key": "tollExpense", "value": "750", "type": "text", "description": "Total toll paid (₹)" },
                { "key": "isHault", "value": "false", "type": "text", "description": "true if the truck was halted/parked overnight" },
                { "key": "isLineCancel", "value": "false", "type": "text", "description": "true if the line/route was cancelled" },
                { "key": "teamMembers", "value": "Raju, Suresh", "type": "text", "description": "Optional — names of other crew members" },
                {
                  "key": "farmerBoxBreakdown",
                  "value": "[{\"farmerName\": \"Farmer A\", \"boxCount\": 80}, {\"farmerName\": \"Farmer B\", \"boxCount\": 60}]",
                  "type": "text",
                  "description": "JSON string — breakdown of boxes per farmer loaded on this truck"
                },
                { "key": "weightSlipPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Required — Weight Bridge slip photo" },
                { "key": "dieselSlipPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Required — Diesel receipt photo" },
                { "key": "unloadSlipPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Required — Unloading receipt / delivery confirmation photo" },
                { "key": "endKmPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Recommended — Odometer photo at destination" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/trips/{{assignmentId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "trips", "{{assignmentId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Submit the final trip report for this assignment.\n\n**Constraints:**\n- Only one Trip per `assignmentId` per driver. Duplicate submission returns `400`.\n- The `driverType` is **auto-detected** from the JWT role: `driver eicher` → `Eicher`.\n- This does **NOT** close the Enquiry. The OM must approve the Packing report to set `Enquiry.status = COMPLETED`.\n\n**After submission:**\n- `Logistics.assignmentStatus` will be updated to `COMPLETED` by the Trip's OM review approval.\n- A PDF system report is auto-generated (`systemReportUrl`)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "PATCH Update Trip Report (After Rejection)",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "totalKm", "value": "510", "type": "text", "description": "Corrected total km" },
                { "key": "tollExpense", "value": "800", "type": "text", "description": "Corrected toll amount" },
                { "key": "weightSlipPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Re-upload corrected weight slip" },
                { "key": "unloadSlipPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Re-upload corrected unload slip" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/trips/{{tripId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "trips", "{{tripId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Update a previously submitted trip report. Only allowed if `reviewStatus` is `PENDING` or `REJECTED`.\n\nUse `:tripId` (the `_id` from the POST Submit response).\n\n**Behaviour:** If `reviewStatus` was `REJECTED`, it is automatically reset to `PENDING` so the OM reviews the corrected report.\n\nOnly supply the fields you want to change — unset fields are left untouched."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "5. History & Reports",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET Paginated Trip History",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/history?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "history"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1", "description": "Page number (default: 1)" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "20", "description": "Records per page (default: 20)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns all completed trip reports for this driver, paginated and sorted newest first."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "GET Monthly Report & KPI",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/reports?month=4&year=2026",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "driver", "reports"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "month", "value": "4", "description": "Month number 1-12 (default: current month)" },
                { "key": "year", "value": "2026", "description": "4-digit year (default: current year)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns a monthly summary:\n- `summary.totalTrips` — number of completed trips\n- `summary.totalKm` — total kilometers driven\n- `summary.totalToll` — total toll expenses (₹)\n- `summary.totalFuelAdvance` — total diesel advance received (₹)\n- `summary.totalHaults` — number of overnight halts\n- `summary.totalLineCancels` — number of line cancellations\n- `dailyTripLog[]` — trips grouped by date"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "GET My Diesel Advances",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/diesel-advance?page=1&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "diesel-advance"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "limit", "value": "10" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns diesel/fuel advances that were issued to this driver by the OM. Useful for the earnings reconciliation screen."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "6. Daily Log — Shift End",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "PATCH End Shift",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                { "key": "endKm", "value": "47320", "type": "text", "description": "Odometer reading at end of shift" },
                { "key": "endKmPhoto", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "📷 Required — Photo of odometer at end of shift" }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/daily-logs/end",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "daily-logs", "end"]
            },
            "description": "Closes the active Day Log for today. Call this at the end of the driver's workday.\n\n**Constraint:** Returns `404` if no active log exists for today."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
